import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    obesity_map = sns.barplot(x='state', y='rate', data=data)
    plt.title("What is the distribution of obesity rates across different states?", wrap=True)
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        obesity_map.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
